---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTABanner from '../components/CTABanner.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Morrisontech"
  description="Over 10 years of IT, cybersecurity, and web development expertise. Australian-owned and operated."
>
  <div class="bg-brand-dark pt-32 pb-16 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">About Morrisontech</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Australian IT expertise, built for the way business works today.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 space-y-12">

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">Who we are</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Morrisontech is an Australian IT business with over 10 years of experience across
        web development, IT consulting, and cybersecurity. We work with small and medium
        businesses across Australia to build fast, professional websites that make a strong
        first impression and turn visitors into customers.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
        We're owner-operated — when you work with Morrisontech, you deal directly with
        the person doing the work. No account managers, no handoffs, no surprises.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">What we do best</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        We specialise in building professional websites and online stores for Australian
        businesses — from simple business sites and landing pages through to full
        e-commerce solutions. Every project is built from scratch to suit your brand
        and your goals.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
        Our background in IT consulting and cybersecurity means we don't just build
        sites that look good — we build sites that are secure, reliable, and
        well-structured from the ground up.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">Why choose us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        We deliver professional results at a fraction of the cost of a traditional agency —
        without cutting corners on quality. Our fixed pricing means you know exactly
        what you're paying upfront, and our Australian-based hosting means your site
        is always supported by someone who answers the phone.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="bg-brand-accent hover:opacity-90 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-md transition-opacity inline-block"
      >
        Let's talk about your project
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <CTABanner />
</Layout>
